# This directory holds Alembic auto-generated migration scripts.
# 
# To generate a new migration after changing ORM models:
#   docker compose exec api alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe your change"
#
# To apply pending migrations:
#   docker compose exec api alembic upgrade head
#
# To roll back the last migration:
#   docker compose exec api alembic downgrade -1
#
# IMPORTANT: Always review auto-generated scripts before applying to production.
# PostGIS-related objects are filtered out in env.py, but check the diff carefully.
